### Infrastructure Type CRUD
###
### Walks through the InfrastructureType lifecycle:
###   1. Create → captures id, asserts configContentType defaults to text/plain when omitted
###   2. Get    → round-trips schema + templates
###   3. Patch  → renames + changes configContentType to text/yaml
###   4. Patch with bad schema → 400 (engine validation)
###   5. Patch with configTemplate set but cmdTemplate empty → 400 (template coupling)
###   6. Delete → 204; subsequent Get → 404 (or 403 per project_api_403_for_missing_rows)

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@adminToken = change-me

### --- Create (ConfigContentType omitted → defaults to text/plain) -----------
# @name createInfraType
POST {{baseUrl}}/infrastructure-types
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "infra-type-e2e",
  "configurationSchema": {
    "properties": {
      "endpoint": {
        "type": "string",
        "label": "Endpoint",
        "required": true
      },
      "port": {
        "type": "integer",
        "label": "Port",
        "default": 443
      }
    }
  },
  "configTemplate": "endpoint={{.endpoint}}\nport={{.port}}\n",
  "cmdTemplate": "curl -fsSL {{.configUrl}} -H 'Authorization: Bearer {{.authToken}}' | sh"
}

@infraTypeId = {{createInfraType.response.body.$.id}}

### --- Get → assert schema, templates, default configContentType -----------
GET {{baseUrl}}/infrastructure-types/{{infraTypeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### --- List with name filter ------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/infrastructure-types?name=infra-type-e2e
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### --- Patch: rename + switch contentType to text/yaml --------------------
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/infrastructure-types/{{infraTypeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "infra-type-e2e-renamed",
  "configContentType": "text/yaml"
}

### --- Patch with empty cmdTemplate while configTemplate is set → 400 -----
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/infrastructure-types/{{infraTypeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cmdTemplate": ""
}

### --- Patch with malformed schema (unknown validator type) → 400 ----------
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/infrastructure-types/{{infraTypeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "configurationSchema": {
    "properties": {
      "endpoint": {
        "type": "string",
        "validators": [
          { "type": "thisValidatorDoesNotExist", "config": {} }
        ]
      }
    }
  }
}

### --- Delete → 204 --------------------------------------------------------
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/infrastructure-types/{{infraTypeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### --- Get after delete → 403/404 (per project_api_403_for_missing_rows) ---
GET {{baseUrl}}/infrastructure-types/{{infraTypeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
